Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.83,0:00:42.38,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NIt's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.21,0:00:45.55,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NI found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.63,0:00:50.26,Main,,0,0,0,,You're her, aren't you?\NYou're my old friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.34,0:00:55.35,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it.\NI loved you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.43,0:00:57.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Didn't we get to take\Na photo together?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.93,0:01:00.31,Main,,0,0,0,,I remember we drank some\Nhoney ginger milk that
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.39,0:01:04.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Mom made for us, and then,\Nwe sang the Love Song.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.77,0:01:06.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you say anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.52,0:01:07.94,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.03,0:01:12.11,Main,,0,0,0,,You're warm. You must\Nstill have a fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.58,0:01:18.45,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA sighs, gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.20,0:01:20.58,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.66,0:01:23.54,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps] That pendant was Mom's.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.63,0:01:25.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Why do you have it,\Nwhen the only one who could
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.75,0:01:29.42,Main,,0,0,0,,is the bear that killed her?\NWhat's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.09,0:01:37.14,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO, LULU]\NYurikuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.22,0:01:39.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Yurikuma Arashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.53,0:03:16.49,Main,,0,0,0,,[YURIIKA]\NI was once unwanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.57,0:03:21.08,Main,,0,0,0,,A lonely bear cub abandoned\Nin the human world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.12,0:03:24.79,Main,,0,0,0,,I found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.13,0:03:31.79,Main,,0,0,0,,[YURIIKA]\NThat was when I met "Him."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.88,0:03:36.55,Main,,0,0,0,,[HIM] Don't worry, I'll shelter\Nyou. This school is my "box."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.80,0:03:42.76,Main,,0,0,0,,[YURIIKA]\NHe really, really liked boxes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.85,0:03:45.10,Main,,0,0,0,,[HIM]\NMy dear Yuriika.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.18,0:03:46.77,Main,,0,0,0,,It's important for\Nyou to understand
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.85,0:03:49.35,Main,,0,0,0,,that this world sullies\Nanything pure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.44,0:03:50.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.65,0:03:53.07,Main,,0,0,0,,If I do this, the flower\Nwill be able to stay
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.15,0:03:55.28,Main,,0,0,0,,unsullied for the\Nrest of eternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.36,0:03:59.70,Main,,0,0,0,,You see, in this world,\Nonly the unsullied have value.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.28,0:04:06.25,Main,,0,0,0,,[YURIIKA]\NGrraow! Grraow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.33,0:04:07.75,Main,,0,0,0,,[HIM]\NYou're incredibly beautiful,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.83,0:04:10.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuriika, and you're so special.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.79,0:04:14.71,Main,,0,0,0,,The most especially\Nprecious treasure I own.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.80,0:04:17.88,Main,,0,0,0,,[YURIIKA] I allowed him\Nto put me into his box.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.01,0:04:21.85,Main,,0,0,0,,[YURIIKA]\NAnd I was happy there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.93,0:04:24.43,Main,,0,0,0,,As long as I stayed\Ninside his box,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.51,0:04:28.23,Main,,0,0,0,,I was an especially precious,\Nunsullied creature.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.31,0:04:31.06,Main,,0,0,0,,I was unwanted no more.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.90,0:04:34.31,Main,,0,0,0,,[YURIIKA]\NBut then, one day...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.74,0:04:40.03,Main,,0,0,0,,[HIM] I'm afraid I've\Nfound my next wonderfully
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.11,0:04:43.32,Main,,0,0,0,,unsullied creature.\NSo, I'm leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.41,0:04:44.87,Main,,0,0,0,,[YURIIKA]\NWait. Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.95,0:04:48.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Please, my precious one.\NPlease don't abandon me here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.00,0:04:52.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Grraow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.75,0:04:54.54,Main,,0,0,0,,[FEMALE VOICE]\NKuma shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.34,0:04:59.47,Main,,0,0,0,,[YURIIKA] In that moment,\NI learned the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.55,0:05:02.84,Main,,0,0,0,,I understood what he\Nwas trying to teach me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.93,0:05:05.76,Main,,0,0,0,,You must box up what\Nis precious to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.85,0:05:08.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, they'll walk\Nright out of your life,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.64,0:05:11.06,Main,,0,0,0,,and wind up sullied.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.14,0:05:15.19,Main,,0,0,0,,From now on,\Nthis school is my box.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.49,0:05:21.07,Main,,0,0,0,,[REIA]\NWhy are you cutting them down?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.87,0:05:26.87,Main,,0,0,0,,I have to cut all these blooms\Nbefore they get sullied.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.95,0:05:29.04,Main,,0,0,0,,If not, I can't put\Nthem in a box.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.16,0:05:32.04,Main,,0,0,0,,[REIA] Why would you\Nwant to box them up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.12,0:05:34.04,Main,,0,0,0,,[YURIIKA]\NSo I can protect these pure,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.13,0:05:36.17,Main,,0,0,0,,precious things from the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.25,0:05:38.75,Main,,0,0,0,,If I protect all the things\Nthat are precious to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.84,0:05:42.09,Main,,0,0,0,,then I'll be special.\NBecause if I am not special...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.18,0:05:44.34,Main,,0,0,0,,[snip]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.43,0:05:47.64,Main,,0,0,0,,[YURIIKA] If I am unwanted,\Nno one will find me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.72,0:05:48.72,Main,,0,0,0,,I found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.81,0:05:53.35,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps] You found me.\NAre you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.44,0:05:56.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes. So get out of\Nthat box of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.52,0:05:58.69,Main,,0,0,0,,If you never open the\Nbox and see and touch
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.77,0:06:01.69,Main,,0,0,0,,your precious collection,\Nthen you might as well
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.78,0:06:03.78,Main,,0,0,0,,just not have anything at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.86,0:06:07.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Might as well not...\NDo you feel empty, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.95,0:06:10.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Like the whole world\Nis invisible?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.25,0:06:11.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Open up your boxes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.87,0:06:15.00,Main,,0,0,0,,I'd love it if you'd show me\Nwhat is truly precious to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.08,0:06:16.08,Main,,0,0,0,,[YURIIKA gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.60,0:06:34.52,Main,,0,0,0,,[YURIIKA] And so Reia and I\Nbecame the best of friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.60,0:06:38.36,Main,,0,0,0,,She gave color to my\Nblank, invisible world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.44,0:06:40.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Everything changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.74,0:06:47.82,Main,,0,0,0,,[YURIIKA] I found all sorts of\Nprecious and wonderful things
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.91,0:06:49.87,Main,,0,0,0,,when I was with Reia.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.08,0:06:55.33,Main,,0,0,0,,[YURIIKA] She allowed\Nherself to be sullied with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.42,0:06:57.08,Main,,0,0,0,,and I was honored.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.29,0:07:03.09,Main,,0,0,0,,[YURIIKA]\NReia, I-I want to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.30,0:07:08.14,Main,,0,0,0,,[YURIIKA]\NI need to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.76,0:07:12.56,Main,,0,0,0,,[YURIIKA]\NI love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.10,0:07:18.02,Main,,0,0,0,,[YURIIKA]\NReia, do you love me, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.10,0:07:20.77,Main,,0,0,0,,[REIA]\NYes, I love you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.86,0:07:23.19,Main,,0,0,0,,[YURIIKA] And we'll be\Nfriends forever, won't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.28,0:07:26.07,Main,,0,0,0,,[REIA]\NYes. Forever and ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.45,0:07:28.11,Main,,0,0,0,,[YURIIKA]\NReia?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.20,0:07:29.99,Main,,0,0,0,,[REIA]\NYes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.07,0:07:31.70,Main,,0,0,0,,[YURIIKA]\NHappy birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.54,0:07:34.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuriika!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.62,0:07:36.41,Main,,0,0,0,,I thought the perfect\Ngift would be
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.50,0:07:38.04,Main,,0,0,0,,to have proof of our friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.12,0:07:40.29,Main,,0,0,0,,[REIA]\NA pledge to never forget love.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.38,0:07:41.71,Main,,0,0,0,,[YURIIKA] As long as\Nyou don't forget love,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.80,0:07:44.05,Main,,0,0,0,,you'll never,\Never be truly alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.13,0:07:45.63,Main,,0,0,0,,And if you never\Ngive up on love,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.71,0:07:49.22,Main,,0,0,0,,even if you lose something,\Nyou'll never be invisible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.30,0:07:55.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Reia. I love you.\NOh, I love you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.10,0:07:57.35,Main,,0,0,0,,[YURIIKA]\NI knew all along
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.44,0:07:59.44,Main,,0,0,0,,that Reia's love was\Ndifferent from mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.52,0:08:04.19,Main,,0,0,0,,I knew it. But, I couldn't help\Nmyself. I wallowed in that
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.27,0:08:08.45,Main,,0,0,0,,sweet, fleeting desire,\Nand it was beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.95,0:08:13.45,Main,,0,0,0,,[baby coos]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.54,0:08:16.66,Main,,0,0,0,,[REIA] Her name is Kureha.\NIt means "red wing".
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.75,0:08:19.71,Main,,0,0,0,,She's perfect, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.79,0:08:24.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Let that go. It seems she\Nwants this pendant for herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.17,0:08:25.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Isn't that sweet?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.59,0:08:27.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.09,0:08:28.93,Main,,0,0,0,,[REIA] Now, Kureha, say hi\Nto one of Mama's best friends
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.01,0:08:30.34,Main,,0,0,0,,in the whole wide world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.43,0:08:32.35,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.43,0:08:37.89,Main,,0,0,0,,[HIM] See. Did I not\Ntell you as much?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.98,0:08:40.56,Main,,0,0,0,,You must box up all\Nyour precious things.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.64,0:08:44.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, they'll be sullied,\Nand you'll lose them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.40,0:08:47.40,Main,,0,0,0,,[HIM] Now Reia's love\Nhas been lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.49,0:08:50.61,Main,,0,0,0,,That baby took it away,\Nand it's your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.70,0:08:54.62,Main,,0,0,0,,You left your box, like a fool,\Nand became sullied.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.70,0:08:56.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Babies are perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.54,0:08:59.96,Main,,0,0,0,,They're among the purest\Nthings in this filthy world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.08,0:09:05.17,Main,,0,0,0,,No more.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.60,0:09:19.23,Main,,0,0,0,,I will give up on love.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.57,0:09:30.03,Main,,0,0,0,,[YURIIKA] I'm sullied,\Nso I'm dirty and empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.11,0:09:31.82,Main,,0,0,0,,I am invisible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.90,0:09:36.70,Main,,0,0,0,,I am not precious enough for\Nsomeone to box up anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.78,0:09:40.33,Main,,0,0,0,,So now. I am a box.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.41,0:09:42.37,Main,,0,0,0,,I've become an empty box,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.46,0:09:45.67,Main,,0,0,0,,wishing for something\Nto fill my void.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.00,0:09:52.09,Main,,0,0,0,,[YURIIKA] The stars rained down,\Nthe world was still invisible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.17,0:09:54.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Then, the Wall of\NSeverance was formed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.72,0:09:58.22,Main,,0,0,0,,And now, we can\Nnever go back again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.31,0:09:59.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Never.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.03,0:10:16.16,Main,,0,0,0,,[YURIIKA]\NReia! Reia! Reia!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.24,0:10:20.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Complete me! I need\Nyou to fill in my gaps!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.33,0:10:24.33,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm so lonely! Please, Reia!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.42,0:10:26.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Please, help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.38,0:10:28.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Reia!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.59,0:10:33.59,Main,,0,0,0,,[REIA] Take this pendant with\Nyou, sweetie. It's a love charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.67,0:10:36.01,Main,,0,0,0,,I know it will help you\Nthe way it helped me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.76,0:10:42.27,Main,,0,0,0,,[YURIIKA]\NGrraow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.35,0:10:43.52,Main,,0,0,0,,[REIA]\NMm?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.60,0:10:46.35,Main,,0,0,0,,[YURIIKA] Why did you\Ngive your pendant away?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.44,0:10:48.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you love her instead of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.27,0:10:50.57,Main,,0,0,0,,[REIA]\NNo! She's just Kureha's friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.65,0:10:53.07,Main,,0,0,0,,[YURIIKA]\NIs she? I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.15,0:10:56.78,Main,,0,0,0,,You threw the proof of our\Nfriendship away! Grraow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.87,0:10:59.91,Main,,0,0,0,,You threw my love away! Grraow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.99,0:11:00.99,Main,,0,0,0,,[REIA screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.29,0:11:05.71,Main,,0,0,0,,[YURIIKA]\NChomp-chomp, Grraow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.79,0:11:10.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Chomp-chomp, Grraow.\NChomp-chomp, Grraow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.38,0:11:15.76,Main,,0,0,0,,[YURIIKA] I ate Reia. I wanted\Nto put her in the box of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.84,0:11:18.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Surely that would complete me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.51,0:11:21.89,Main,,0,0,0,,At least, that's what I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.77,0:11:33.94,Main,,0,0,0,,[YURIIKA] Even after eating\NReia, I felt starved.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.03,0:11:37.74,Main,,0,0,0,,The emptiness inside me\Nstill me wasn't filled.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.82,0:11:41.83,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA] Before I knew it, I\Nfound myself interrogating her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.91,0:11:45.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Good for you. Did she\Nhave an excuse at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.96,0:11:47.54,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NWell...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.75,0:11:53.09,Main,,0,0,0,,The night my mom\Nwas killed by a bear,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.17,0:11:56.67,Main,,0,0,0,,the pendant she was\Nwearing disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.76,0:11:59.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Why in the world do\Nyou have it, Ginko?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.22,0:12:01.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Not right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.01,0:12:05.35,Main,,0,0,0,,The only thing she would say was\Nshe couldn't tell me right then,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.43,0:12:06.89,Main,,0,0,0,,and when I woke up this morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.98,0:12:09.77,Main,,0,0,0,,both of them had left\Nwithout saying goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.15,0:12:13.77,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA gasps]\NWhat are these?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.86,0:12:15.74,Main,,0,0,0,,[YURIIKA] This is the\Nevidence we need to prove
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.82,0:12:18.49,Main,,0,0,0,,they're actually bears\Ndisguised as humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.57,0:12:19.78,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.86,0:12:22.41,Main,,0,0,0,,[YURIIKA] And as for\Nthat Ginko Yurishiro one,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.49,0:12:24.83,Main,,0,0,0,,she's the bear with\NReia's pendant.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.91,0:12:27.29,Main,,0,0,0,,You think she's the\Nbear that killed Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.37,0:12:29.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes. Of that I\Nhave no doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.71,0:12:30.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.88,0:12:32.29,Main,,0,0,0,,[YURIIKA]\NYou were young,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.38,0:12:34.67,Main,,0,0,0,,and she got close to you by\Nsaying she was your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.75,0:12:37.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Then, she took away the most\Nprecious thing in your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.55,0:12:39.80,Main,,0,0,0,,She murdered your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.88,0:12:42.64,Main,,0,0,0,,We can't expect love\Nor friendship from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.72,0:12:44.10,Main,,0,0,0,,They must be excluded.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.18,0:12:46.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Excluded.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.73,0:12:51.02,Main,,0,0,0,,[YURIIKA] Hm. That's\Nright, and by the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.10,0:12:53.94,Main,,0,0,0,,since you stole\NReia's love from me,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.02,0:12:58.19,Main,,0,0,0,,that crime will have to be\Npaid for with your flesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.28,0:13:01.49,Main,,0,0,0,,There's no escaping,\Nnow, Kureha Tsubaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.57,0:13:03.58,Main,,0,0,0,,You're going to be my bride.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.66,0:13:05.74,Main,,0,0,0,,My bride-in-the-box.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.43,0:13:25.10,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU]\N"Ginko Yurishiro,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.18,0:13:27.72,Main,,0,0,0,,I know all about the grave\Ncrime you committed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.81,0:13:30.52,Main,,0,0,0,,I know what you did.\NYou were the one who..."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.60,0:13:32.02,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.98,0:13:36.73,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU]\NHey, Ginko?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.82,0:13:41.15,Main,,0,0,0,,How about we go back to\Nthe other side of the wall?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.24,0:13:44.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Lulu doesn't think it matters\Nhow true your love is,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.32,0:13:46.74,Main,,0,0,0,,when she knows\Nyou're a bear, growl,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.83,0:13:48.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Kure-pie won't forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.29,0:13:53.12,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU] Promise Kisses only\Nexist in picture books.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.21,0:13:55.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Kumaria is the\Ngoddess of the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.88,0:13:58.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Her job is to separate\Nbears and humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.63,0:14:01.72,Main,,0,0,0,,She'd never let us\Nall be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.80,0:14:04.72,Main,,0,0,0,,I made you give up on\Nkisses for me, Lulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.80,0:14:08.72,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't go back to our side,\Nnow. Growl, growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.81,0:14:11.81,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU]\NEven if it means a grave sin?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.89,0:14:12.64,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO]\NHm?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.73,0:14:14.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl, growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.31,0:14:17.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Lulu knows what you did, Ginko,\Nso please. Let's just go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.98,0:14:21.24,Main,,0,0,0,,If Kure-pie finds out the whole\Ntruth, you'll never get love.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.32,0:14:23.32,Main,,0,0,0,,But you won't be able\Nto do a Promise Kiss
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.40,0:14:25.32,Main,,0,0,0,,without telling her\Nthe whole truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.87,0:14:28.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Come on! Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.37,0:14:31.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Even if you give up on love,\NLulu will still love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.29,0:14:33.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Lulu doesn't care if\Nshe can't ever kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.66,0:14:35.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Just so long as you're with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.29,0:14:38.54,Main,,0,0,0,,But, Lulu, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.88,0:14:44.05,Main,,0,0,0,,[YURIIKA]\NYes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.13,0:14:46.93,Main,,0,0,0,,[LIFE SEXY]\NIs your love the real thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.01,0:14:49.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.47,0:14:51.98,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NAbsolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.06,0:14:55.39,Main,,0,0,0,,[LIFE SEXY] This is a challenge\Nfrom the Wall of Severance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.48,0:14:58.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Kureha Tsubaki,\Nif your love is true,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.77,0:15:04.53,Main,,0,0,0,,go to the roof immediately.\NThe bears are waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.61,0:15:06.36,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NI'm on my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.37,0:15:15.37,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA] We were friends.\NYes, I loved her, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.42,0:15:19.92,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NI'll never forgive those bears!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.00,0:15:22.46,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll ruin them. Every one!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.13,0:15:26.01,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU]\NWait! Please, Ginko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.09,0:15:28.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Lulu really doesn't mind if\Nyou love Kure-pie! Growl!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.05,0:15:30.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Just don't leave her,\Nplease don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.97,0:15:34.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Ginko! Ginko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.31,0:15:37.81,Main,,0,0,0,,[LIFE SEXY] Give yourself\Nover to the humans,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.90,0:15:40.61,Main,,0,0,0,,and your love will be approved.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.69,0:15:42.86,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO]\NI'm so sorry, Lulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.94,0:15:47.91,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU]\NGinko! Growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.33,0:15:55.62,Main,,0,0,0,,[LIFE COOL]\NShe's so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.71,0:15:59.04,Main,,0,0,0,,However, I'm not entirely sure\Nthis was the right thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.13,0:16:02.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't be so dramatic, we're\Nonly doing what has to be done
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.09,0:16:05.22,Main,,0,0,0,,in order find out whose love\Nis true. Sparkle, sparkle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.30,0:16:08.47,Main,,0,0,0,,[LIFE COOL] But it still\Nseems horribly cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.55,0:16:10.26,Main,,0,0,0,,[LIFE SEXY]\NOrder, in the court, please,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.35,0:16:14.06,Main,,0,0,0,,we swell here, in the space\Nbetween human and bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.14,0:16:17.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Everything must be done\Naccording to Kumaria's will.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.60,0:16:19.77,Main,,0,0,0,,--For that is sexy.\N--[thunder rumbles]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.85,0:16:21.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Perhaps it will rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.52,0:16:23.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Shaba-da-doo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.11,0:16:32.08,Main,,0,0,0,,[YURIIKA]\NThe time has come at last.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.16,0:16:36.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Come to me, Kureha Tsubaki.\NAfter all, I cast aside beardom
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.96,0:16:40.21,Main,,0,0,0,,to become human,\Nand I did it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.04,0:16:47.80,Main,,0,0,0,,[LIFE SEXY] Defendant bear\NYuriika Hakonaka, I ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.88,0:16:53.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Will you give up on boxes?\NOr, will you give up on Love?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.14,0:16:56.64,Main,,0,0,0,,I will never give up on boxes,\Nso, I'll give up on love.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.73,0:16:57.60,Main,,0,0,0,,[LIFE SEXY]\NMm?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.68,0:16:58.89,Main,,0,0,0,,[LIFE COOL, LIFE BEAUTY]\NMm?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.98,0:17:00.73,Main,,0,0,0,,[YURIIKA]\NPlease make me human!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.81,0:17:04.19,Main,,0,0,0,,I'd like to be there to see\NKureha Tsubaki grow up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.27,0:17:07.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Reia's love is still\Nalive inside that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.82,0:17:11.57,Main,,0,0,0,,And I want to fill up the box\Nof myself with that love!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.66,0:17:13.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you\Nwon't regret that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.62,0:17:15.95,Main,,0,0,0,,You realize if you are\Ngiven what you ask for,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.04,0:17:18.20,Main,,0,0,0,,you'll be doomed to be\Na box for all eternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.29,0:17:21.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Reia gave my love away to some\Nother cub like it was nothing,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.17,0:17:23.42,Main,,0,0,0,,and I've made the choice\Nto hold it against her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.50,0:17:25.50,Main,,0,0,0,,I'd rather be a\Nbox than forgive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.59,0:17:29.51,Main,,0,0,0,,[LIFE SEXY] I see. I shall\Nnow declare the verdict.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.59,0:17:32.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuri approved!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.01,0:17:38.27,Main,,0,0,0,,[YURIIKA]\NYuri approved!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.85,0:17:44.02,Main,,0,0,0,,[FEMALE VOICE]\N♪ Kuma ga aku. ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.11,0:17:49.94,Main,,0,0,0,,[panting] Miss Yuriika,\Nyou're here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.03,0:17:52.40,Main,,0,0,0,,I've been waiting for\Nyou, sweet Kureha.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.49,0:17:53.82,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NWhat for?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.91,0:17:55.87,Main,,0,0,0,,You'll find her over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.62,0:18:01.29,Main,,0,0,0,,It's you, Ginko.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.37,0:18:04.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Be careful. Remember, she\Nis the bear who killed Reia.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.63,0:18:06.63,Main,,0,0,0,,She is our mortal enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.71,0:18:09.01,Main,,0,0,0,,You killed my mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.09,0:18:14.43,Main,,0,0,0,,[YURIIKA] Take her out.\NGinko betrayed both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.51,0:18:17.35,Main,,0,0,0,,I know she claimed to be your\Nfriend, but it was just a trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.43,0:18:21.93,Main,,0,0,0,,A trick she used to take away\Nwhat was most precious to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.27,0:18:25.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Kureha.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.15,0:18:29.65,Main,,0,0,0,,You ate my mother. How could\Nyou do something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.73,0:18:32.28,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO]\NI didn't eat her. Growl, growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.36,0:18:33.49,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NYes, you did!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.57,0:18:35.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Why else would you be\Nwearing her pendant?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.99,0:18:37.83,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO]\NYour mother gave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.91,0:18:39.95,Main,,0,0,0,,She said it was a love charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.04,0:18:41.83,Main,,0,0,0,,She gave you\Na love charm?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.91,0:18:47.13,Main,,0,0,0,,I am a bear, but somehow,\Nwe still managed to be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.21,0:18:50.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl, growl. Until one day,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.80,0:18:53.92,Main,,0,0,0,,you and I couldn't\Nbe together anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.10,0:18:58.97,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO] You started to\Nbelieve that all bears
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.06,0:19:01.31,Main,,0,0,0,,were the enemies of humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.39,0:19:03.73,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NObviously. Bears kill people.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.81,0:19:06.98,Main,,0,0,0,,My own mother, included!\NThey are enemies!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.06,0:19:08.57,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO]\NYou're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.65,0:19:12.90,Main,,0,0,0,,I was just an unwanted-bear, but\Nyou found me and saved my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.99,0:19:15.40,Main,,0,0,0,,You approved me,\Nand gave me love!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.49,0:19:17.03,Main,,0,0,0,,It's true! Growl, growl!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.12,0:19:18.99,Main,,0,0,0,,It is not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.08,0:19:22.83,Main,,0,0,0,,I refuse to forget the love\NI got from you that day,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.91,0:19:26.92,Main,,0,0,0,,and I refuse to give\Nup on the love I felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.00,0:19:31.50,Main,,0,0,0,,That's why I crossed the wall.\NI'm here for you, Kureha.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.59,0:19:34.59,Main,,0,0,0,,I wanted to be true friends\Nwith you once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.67,0:19:38.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Really, that's\Nwhy you're here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.93,0:19:40.01,Main,,0,0,0,,[YURIIKA]\NDon't listen to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.10,0:19:42.39,Main,,0,0,0,,She's a liar and\Na murderer bear!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.47,0:19:45.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Think of all the girls in\Nyour class that she killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.48,0:19:48.48,Main,,0,0,0,,I wanted to protect Kureha\Nfrom the Invisible Storm!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.56,0:19:52.03,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't forgive those\Nwho try to exclude her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.11,0:19:55.15,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm a bear.\NWhat else could I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.24,0:19:56.74,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NOh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.82,0:19:59.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you as much? Bears\Ndon't feel love or friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.08,0:20:03.45,Main,,0,0,0,,They're sullied beasts.\NAnd that is their true nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.54,0:20:06.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Do it, already. Shoot that\Nthing until it's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.87,0:20:08.75,Main,,0,0,0,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.83,0:20:11.46,Main,,0,0,0,,--[GINKO] It's okay, Kureha.\N--[KUREHA gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.54,0:20:13.05,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO]\NI finally understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.13,0:20:15.67,Main,,0,0,0,,When Lady Kumaria told me\Nabout the Promise Kiss,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.76,0:20:17.68,Main,,0,0,0,,she was actually talking\Nabout that bullet
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.76,0:20:20.30,Main,,0,0,0,,in the chamber of your gun.\NGrowl, growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.39,0:20:21.64,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.72,0:20:23.93,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO] I'll accept\Nthis as a criminal bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.02,0:20:25.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Hopefully, it'll prove to you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.47,0:20:27.02,Main,,0,0,0,,the love I have\Nis the real thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.10,0:20:29.44,Main,,0,0,0,,If this is the only way to\Nbecome true friends with you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.52,0:20:32.36,Main,,0,0,0,,again, then I will embrace it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.44,0:20:34.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Do it! Why you hesitating?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.23,0:20:36.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Punish that criminal\Nbear right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.03,0:20:43.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Give me the Promise Kiss.\NI'm ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.24,0:20:46.25,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.76,0:21:02.30,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NPromise Kiss? From me, to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.39,0:21:03.81,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO]\NAnd me to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.89,0:21:08.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Then, everything will awaken,\Nand it will all change.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.91,0:21:27.49,Main,,0,0,0,,What do you think\Nyou're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.58,0:21:30.37,Main,,0,0,0,,I... can't shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.46,0:21:32.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't be absurd!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.59,0:21:37.05,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA] Killing her isn't\Ngoing to bring Mom back to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.13,0:21:38.63,Main,,0,0,0,,It won't change anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.71,0:21:40.30,Main,,0,0,0,,[YURIIKA]\NYou mustn't forgive her!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.38,0:21:43.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Give this woman-eating bear\Nthe Bullet of Judgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.30,0:21:45.35,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NI can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.43,0:21:47.93,Main,,0,0,0,,How could I when Ginko\Nwas the one who saved me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.02,0:21:51.35,Main,,0,0,0,,from the Invisible Storm?\NShe jumped into the fire, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.44,0:21:54.44,Main,,0,0,0,,She risked her life to protect\NSumika's letter for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.52,0:21:56.15,Main,,0,0,0,,You fool. That beast is just
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.23,0:21:58.36,Main,,0,0,0,,a criminal bear\Npretending to be pure!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.44,0:22:01.24,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't care!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.32,0:22:02.28,Main,,0,0,0,,--[LULU] Kure-pie!\N--[KUREHA] Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.36,0:22:03.37,Main,,0,0,0,,[YURIIKA gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.91,0:22:06.95,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NLulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.12,0:22:12.66,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU]\NKure-pie. Lulu knows the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.75,0:22:14.75,Main,,0,0,0,,She found out what\NGinko did to Sumika.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.83,0:22:16.13,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.21,0:22:20.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes. Ginko committed\Na grave crime, growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.46,0:22:22.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Ginko is the reason\Nwhy Sumika is--
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.55,0:22:24.39,Main,,0,0,0,,[thunder strikes]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.35,0:22:34.77,Main,,0,0,0,,[inaudible]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.85,0:22:36.61,Main,,0,0,0,,[thunder rumbles]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.69,0:22:42.40,Main,,0,0,0,,[inaudible]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.66,0:22:52.41,Main,,0,0,0,,How could you, Ginko?\NI'll never forgive you bears!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.50,0:22:55.75,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll ruin you, now. Every one!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.92,0:23:04.17,Main,,0,0,0,,[REIA] Tell me.\NIs your love the real thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.26,0:23:05.97,Main,,0,0,0,,[gun shot]
